{"body": "There is a rampant discussion on this topic in issue #1159. My personal opinion is that this is so easy to implement, any non-standard interaction (field name, encryption method, etc.) should just have its own implementation.\r\n\r\nIf absolutely needed, any options to `has_secure_password` should be passed in a options hash, e.g. `has_secure_password :column => \"pwd\"`.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1296556", "created_at": "2011-06-03T13:05:53Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1440#issuecomment-1296556", "updated_at": "2011-06-03T13:05:53Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 1440, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/dasch", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a9cc05e6a7866e5fa9a7d107b5070174?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc6862d63b17d713ee14f3a405d9fde77.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/received_events", "gravatar_id": "a9cc05e6a7866e5fa9a7d107b5070174", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "dasch", "type": "User", "id": 6351, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5238551ebd3543c1510119ea"}, "id": 1296556, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/1440"}
